        "Each iteration diagnoses from traces, where scores aggregate performance over categories.",
        "Each iteration then experiments with a targeted harness change scoped to one change at a time.",
        "The loop validates that changes helped pass new evals while avoiding regressions.",
        "Common harness changes include prompt and instruction updates and adding or updating tool descriptions."
    ]
}
