        "Experience replay maintains a buffer of 50,000 historical interactions sampled using prioritized replay with alpha=0.6.",
        "The pipeline runs on a dedicated Kubernetes cluster with auto-scaling based on replay buffer utilization.",
        "Each consolidation cycle takes approximately 4 hours on 8 A100 GPUs.",
        "The system checkpoints every 1,000 gradient steps to enable rollback.",
